<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText"><p>A mysterious note is found with some information about Halloween in Norrath...</p><br><br><blockquote>Starting this Friday (Oct. 28) An old man may be found that will teach Norrathians how to trick-or-treat and your practice will yield tasty candy treats. Meanwhile, a creepy bone collector will request help on collecting several rare bone artifacts and a story teller will spin some rather frightening tales, with the proper ticket of admission. In other areas, the Halflings are more hungry than usual and their craving for pumpkin will lead to a vampire mishap. Seek out Zigand Ribshard in the Plane of Knowledge.  He may have some information!</blockquote></td></tr>
