<tr><td align="left" class="newsCategory">CommunityNews - <font align="left" class="newsDate">9:07 AM PST</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText">Here's the announcement:<br><br><blockquote>Howdy folks!<br><br>Most of you don't know me, but I'm Kwip, and I run a small MMORPG humor site, NeenerNeener.Net. Previously, my stories & comics had dealt with other worlds, but we recently re-launched, and part of that re-launching was me taking the dive back into EQ. Today's story deals with that, so hopefully you'll find it amusing and share it with your readers and invite them to stop by www.neenerneener.net and check us out.<br><br>Thanks!<br>Kwip</blockquote>Enjoy, and have fun!<br></td></tr>
