<tr><td align="left" class="newsCategory">CommunityNews - <font align="left" class="newsDate">9:25 AM PST</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText">For those of you awaiting the game you can find it in stores soon.<br><br>Here's a snippet from the press release:<br><br><blockquote>SAN DIEGO, CA - January 28, 2004 - Sony Online Entertainment Inc. (SOE), a worldwide leader in massively multiplayer online gaming, today announced that Champions of Norrath(tm) has gone gold. Champions of Norrath, available exclusively on the PlayStation(r)2 computer entertainment system, will ship to U.S. and Canadian retail stores on February 11, 2004.</blockquote>Enjoy!<br><br></td></tr>
