<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText">Questions about the new Graphics Engine are answered!<br><br><blockquote>Lepidus: The game mechanics are still among the best, but the graphics of EverQuest mark its age. Are there any plans to fully update the graphics of EverQuest to compete with other games? <br><br>Alan VanCouvering: Yes! We are already in the process of upgrading the EverQuest graphics engine. We will be making announcements as to its rollout in the next few months!</blockquote>Click <a href="http://<a href="http://www.eqvault.com" target="_blank">EverQuest Vault</a>.ign.com/articles/456/456932p1.html?fromint=1">Here</a> for the full interview. <br><br>The new engine is finally confirmed, what do you think of it?  <br><br></td></tr>
